  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;The enlarged part of the dwellinghouse would have a single storey and extend beyond the rear wall of the original dwellinghouse by more than 3 metres in the case of terrace / semi-detached dwellinghouse &amp;amp; the enlarged part of the dwellinghouse would extend beyond a wall forming a side elevation of the original dwellinghouse, and would have a width greater than half the width of the original dwellinghouse. As such, the proposed extension would not constitute permitted development by virtue of the Town and Country Planning (General Permitted Development) (England) Order 2015 Schedule 2, Part 1, Class A.1(f)(i) &amp;amp; (j) (iii).&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;"
